flowchart TD
A([User Goal])-->B[Planner]
B-->C[Generate Initial Investigation Tasks]
C-->D[Task Queue]
D-->E[Select Next Task]
E-->F[Tool Decision]
F-->G[Search Corpus / Read File]
G-->H[Observation]
H-->I{Observation Type}
I-->|Finding|J[Mark Task Complete]
I-->|Conflict|K[Insert New Task]
I-->|Gap|L[Retry]
L-->E
K-->D
J-->N{More Tasks?}
N-->|Yes|E
N-->|No|O[Final Report]
